Compatibility validation
-------------------------
The cryptographic primitives are verified byte-for-byte against published test
vectors (AES FIPS-197; Twofish and Serpent official vectors; AES-XTS IEEE 1619;
AES-CBC NIST SP 800-38A; RIPEMD-160/Whirlpool reference; PBKDF2 RFC 6070) via the
native KAT harness and the managed xUnit suite.
